statements: SELECT * FROM charging_sessions;
SELECT charging_session_id, user_id, start_time FROM charging_sessions WHERE energy_consumed > 100;
SELECT user_id, charging_session_id, end_time FROM charging_sessions ORDER BY end_time DESC;
SELECT charging_station_id, COUNT(*) AS total_sessions FROM charging_sessions GROUP BY charging_station_id;
SELECT user_id, SUM(energy_consumed) AS total_energy_consumed FROM charging_sessions GROUP BY user_id HAVING SUM(energy_consumed) > 500;

SELECT user_id, start_time, energy_consumed FROM charging_sessions WHERE energy_consumed > 50 ORDER BY start_time DESC;

SELECT charging_session_id, start_time, end_time, energy_consumed, charging_station_id FROM charging_sessions WHERE start_time >= '2022-01-01' AND end_time <= '2022-12-31' ORDER BY energy_consumed DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT user_id FROM charging_sessions WHERE energy_consumed BETWEEN 20 AND 30 ORDER BY user_id ASC;
